'''甲醇锂'''是[[锂|锂]]的[[甲醇盐|甲醇盐]]，化学式为LiOCH<sub>3</sub>。它可由金属锂和[[甲醇|甲醇]]反应得到：
: 2 Li + 2 CH<sub>3</sub>OH → 2 CH<sub>3</sub>OLi + H<sub>2</sub>↑
它是锂和甲醇反应的唯一产物。而相应的钠、钾类似物除了生成相应的醇盐之外，还可以产生醇盐的甲醇合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Chemical Society (Resumed)|language=en|issn=0368-1769|date=1960|pages=4270|doi=10.1039/jr9600004270|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=jr9600004270|title=835. A physicochemical investigation of the methoxides of lithium, sodium, and potassium|accessdate=2020-08-14|author=P. J. Wheatley}}</ref>它和[[硝酸银|硝酸银]]、[[高氯酸银|高氯酸银]]等银盐在无水甲醇中反应，生成金属银。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthesis and Reactivity in Inorganic and Metal-Organic Chemistry|volume=7|issue=2|language=en|issn=0094-5714|date=1977-01|pages=111–122|doi=10.1080/00945717708055947|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00945717708055947|title=The Instability of Silver Alkoxides|accessdate=2020-08-14|author=Roger S. Macomber, John C. Ford, Jeffrey H. Wenzel}}</ref>

甲醇锂可用于制备其它锂化合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Non-Crystalline Solids|volume=356|issue=43|language=en|date=2010-09|pages=2263–2267|doi=10.1016/j.jnoncrysol.2010.08.017|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022309310005855|title=Devitrification behavior and structure of Li2O–B2O3–Al2O3 composite gels from metal alkoxides|accessdate=2020-08-14|author=Shengchun Li, B. Li, X.B. Qi, J.J. Wei}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=631|issue=10|language=de|issn=0044-2313|date=2005-08|pages=1741–1742|doi=10.1002/zaac.200500098|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/zaac.200500098|title=- ein neues lösliches Tetrachalkogenoniobat|accessdate=2020-08-14|author=Robert Feuerhake, Hülya Sahin, Dieter Fenske}}</ref>
